cross: Papiopedilum malipoense x Paphiopedilum Fumi's Delight

measurements.description:
Two pleasing flowers on two 39.0-cm inflorescences; dorsal and synsepal chartreuse, faintly
tessellated darker chartreuse; petals chartreuse, tessellated light mahogany; pouch very light
green, rim blushed raspberry pink, interior stippled maroon, visible on exterior; staminode spade
shaped, white, proximal margin blushed light maroon, distal two-thirds overlaid dark maroon;
substance firm; texture matte.
